  <summary date="2020-09-23T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Rohingya Genocide Determination Act of 2020

This bill requires the Department of State to report to Congress an assessment of the persecution of the Rohingya, a predominantly Muslim group in Burma (Myanmar), by Burma's military and security forces, and whether the situation constitutes genocide under U.S. law.</summary>
